      <abstract>
        <p>Euro declines, settling at 86.84 cents, down from 86.92; graph; chart (S)9</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>THE EURO FALLS. The euro drifted lower yesterday, but the damage was limited as dealers struck a cautious tone ahead of a long U.S. holiday weekend. In New York, the euro settled at 86.84 cents, down from 86.92.</p>
      </block>
